what_you_do: Tammy Workman-Lopez is a senior leadership coach who specializes in mindset development and behavioral insight to support leaders in navigating complex transitions, high-stakes environments, and people challenges with greater clarity and confidence.
who_you_serve: Tammy has coached leaders across healthcare, education, nonprofit, and entrepreneurial sectors, including senior leaders, small business CEOs, and high-potential professionals stepping into larger roles.
social_proof: Tammy holds certifications in the E3 Behavioral Assessment and Blindspotting frameworks through Behavioral Essentials, as well as in programs like Mind Power and Magnetic Mind. She is also a published author and contributor to several collaborative works, including titles that have reached the New York Times bestseller list.
